---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout 
  title="Terms of Service" 
  description="Terms and conditions for using Cogintech's AI-powered inspection analysis platform"
>
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <p class="text-sm text-foreground/60 mb-8">Last updated: January 1, 2025</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-cogintech-blue">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing or using Cogintech's services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and all applicable laws and regulations.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-cogintech-blue">2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Cogintech provides AI-powered equipment integrity analysis services, including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Automated inspection data analysis</li>
        <li>Multi-agent AI verification systems</li>
        <li>Report generation and delivery</li>
        <li>Natural language query interfaces</li>
        <li>Historical data integration</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-cogintech-blue">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">You agree to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide accurate and complete information</li>
        <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials</li>
        <li>Use the service only for lawful purposes</li>
        <li>Not attempt to reverse engineer or compromise our systems</li>
        <li>Comply with all applicable regulations and standards</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-cogintech-blue">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content, features, and functionality of our service are owned by Cogintech and are protected by copyright, trademark, and other intellectual property laws.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-cogintech-blue">5. Data Ownership</h2>
      <p>You retain ownership of all data you provide to our service. We use your data solely to provide our analysis services and do not claim ownership or use it for other purposes without your consent.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-cogintech-blue">6. Service Availability</h2>
      <p>While we strive for maximum uptime, we do not guarantee uninterrupted service availability. We may perform maintenance or updates that temporarily affect service access.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-cogintech-blue">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>Cogintech's liability is limited to the amount paid for our services. We are not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of our service.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-cogintech-blue">8. Professional Judgment</h2>
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-4">
        <p class="text-yellow-800">
          <strong>Important:</strong> Our AI analysis is designed to assist and enhance professional judgment, not replace it. 
          All critical decisions should involve qualified professionals and comply with applicable industry standards and regulations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-cogintech-blue">9. Termination</h2>
      <p>Either party may terminate the service agreement with appropriate notice as specified in the service contract. Upon termination, access to the service will be revoked.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-cogintech-blue">10. Contact Information</h2>
      <p>For questions about these Terms of Service, contact us at:</p>
      <div class="bg-cogintech-blue/5 p-4 rounded-lg mt-4">
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> legal@cogintech.ai</p>
        <p><strong>Address:</strong> Cogintech Ltd., Houston, Texas</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
      <p class="text-sm text-blue-800">
        <strong>Note:</strong> These are sample terms of service for demonstration purposes. 
        Actual terms should be reviewed by legal counsel and tailored to your specific business model and jurisdiction.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>